200 Ranged Attack and Smart is to hit as hard as possible 
 200 Speed with Nimble is to be as fast as possible, and outspeeds Nimble Phagenaut and below

 Note: 1 Gamma Pulse = 2 Power Focuses 
 16 Ranged Defense gives Protogon an M Attack boost 
 52 HP is leftovers
